message.content: cs.SD, cs.SD is the most likely category as it deals with sound and music computing. cs.CL is also likely as it deals with natural language processing and language modelling. cs.LG is another possibility as it deals with machine learning and neural networks. cs.AI and cs.IR are less likely but still possible as they deal with artificial intelligence and information retrieval, respectively, which could be relevant to the topic of automatic chord recognition.
